text: Geoffery Burnside (born 5 November 1950) is a former Bahamian cyclist. He competed in the sprint event at the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1950 births Category:Living people Category:Bahamian male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of the Bahamas Category:Cyclists at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
